# NETWORK::NETWORK_GET_PLAYER_FROM_GAMER_HANDLE

## Parameters
* **GAMER_HANDLE\*** gamerHandle

## Returns
* **PLAYER_INDEX**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns player index of player in session matching handle (-1 if not in session)
